    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Labor union people today are claim\ning that the plumbers strike will soon\nend. The trades council has taken up\nthe gauntlet and are concentrating all\nefforts against the boss plumbers of the\ncity. Frantic efforts are being made\nby them and the strike thus far has\nproven that the bosses are more than\never determined the strikers will not\nwin if the difficulty lasts for whole\nyear.\n\n\nThe trades council for a while let\neverything run along in very lax\nmanner and now. at this late date,\nthey have concluded things have gone\nquite far enough and that drastic mea-\nsures must now be used. As planned,\nnext Tuesday when the council meets,"
    }
